org.knime.core.node.streamable

Interface StreamableFunctionProducer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppendVariableToTable2NodeModel, CaseConvertNodeModel, CellSplitterByPosNodeModel, ColCombine2NodeModel, CollectionCreate2NodeModel, ColumnComparatorNodeModel, ColumnMergerNodeModel, ColumnResorterNodeModel, ConstantValueColumnNodeModel, DoubleToIntNodeModel, RegexSplitNodeModel, RenameNodeModel, RoundDoubleNodeModel, SearchReplaceDictNodeModel, SimpleStreamableFunctionNodeModel, SimpleStreamableFunctionWithInternalsNodeModel, StringReplacerNodeModel, StringToNumberNodeModel

    public interface StreamableFunctionProducer
    Interface implemented by NodeModel to narrow the return type of NodeModel.createStreamableOperator(PartitionInfo, PortObjectSpec[]).

    It helps the framework to distinguish between general purpose operators and functions, which can be handled more efficiently.

    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Bernd Wiswedel, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
    No public API: not to be extended by clients
    Pending API, see StreamableOperator.
